description: Human Unitec International Inc. engages in the project financing, development, and asset management activities. It finances and develops medical and wellness, renewable, water desalination, and alternative energy projects, as well as emerging growth companies. The company is developing a project for the construction of the of the technology GRONE system, which is a versatile waste sorting center that acts as a recycling center and power plant. Human Unitec International Inc. is based in Boston, Massachusetts.
